Description: Functions to simulate water fluxes, soil moisture and drought stress using the 
    LWF-Brook90 hydrologic model. Several functions provide for convenient simulation set-up 
    and model execution, as well as parallelisation of multi-run simulations.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
